<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Brainni!</title>
    <style>
        /* Apply box-sizing globally */
        *, *:before, *:after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scrollbar */
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #0056b3; /* Updated background color */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative; /* Ensures the nav bar is a positioning context */
            color: black;
            border-bottom: 0.5px solid white;
        }
        .logo {
            height: 120px; /* Adjust based on your actual logo's dimensions */
            position: absolute;
            top: -10px;
            left: 10px;
            border-radius: 80px;
        }
        .nav-links {
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px; /* Aligns links to the far right */
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            
        }

       
        a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: 1px solid #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }
        a:hover {
            background-color: #0077cc;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .content {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            background: url('../images/young-kid-streaming-online.jpg') no-repeat center center; /* Add your background image here */
            background-size: cover; /* Cover the entire .content area */
        }
        .card {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* Semi-transparent white background */
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        #chabot{
            background-color: #0077cc !important;
        }
        .footer {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <img src="../images/logo.png" alt="Brainni Logo" class="logo">
        <div class="nav-links">
            <% if (!user) { %>
                <a href="/login">Login</a>
                <a href="/register">Register</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/profile">My Profile</a>
                <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="card">
            <p>Or test our beta version of Brainni Chat to see how our tailored solutions can enhance your learning.</p>
            <a id="chatbot" style="background-color: #0077cc;" href="/chatbot">Try Brainni Chat</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Thank you for visiting Brainni! We hope you enjoy your educational journey with us.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
